Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日報我能聯繫的人都聯繫了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I spoke to everyone I know at the Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人告訴我誰給的照片  但肯定是雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody's naming sources, but it has to be Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉樂威要出面迴應嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is Galloway going on the record?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的  他會先和我們接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wouldn't. Not without speaking to us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-最好確保這一點    -我這就去和亞當說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Let's be sure about that.   - I'll talk to Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許避免和他接觸會更好些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's smarter to avoid contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總得有人出面迴應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Somebody has to respond,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是他就是我們  或者一起迴應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whether it's him, or us, or both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得協調好  小心應對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to coordinate, and do it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事交給我吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先想好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, let's just think this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有問題的  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got it covered, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還去辦公室嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Head back to the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你還是在家辦公比較好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think you should work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出門的話  很難躲開媒體\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't avoid the press if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那好  你把好門    -好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- All right. You hold down the fort.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽克萊爾差遣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you follow Claire's lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事會解決的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll shut this down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能讓人質疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There can't be any doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再過一遍時間線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's walk through a timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你首次見他是什麼時候    -惠特尼雙年展\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- So you first met him when? -In Whitney Biennial...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事傷害了我們兩個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This hurts us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要著手去處理的人不是我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it's not my wound to suture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾必須親自動手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire must be the surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有她才能穩住局勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only she can stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有盤子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know we got them plates in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按你要求的改好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All the changes you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多給你5%的追補股份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gave you five more points on the post-recoupment share.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,營銷宣傳材料需要你認可\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Approval over all the marketing materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀泉旗艦店的人事也要經你認可\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Approval over the staff hires of the flagship in Silver Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-接下來做什麼    -簽字就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- So, what next?   - You sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-然後我九萬五就到手了    -這週末吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- And I get my $95,000?   - By the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得先把錢從主賬戶注入公司賬戶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just have to wire it from our main account into the LLC,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還得核對賬目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}had cash years to check for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想給你看看這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是醬料瓶的樣品\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a mockup of the bottle design.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經開始為銀泉店的外觀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we already started on the concept layouts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行概念設計了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for the Silver Spring location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼牆氈都裂開了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why's that linoleum peeling up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追求真實感啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To make it seem real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望比這漂亮些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted it to look nicer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以改掉牆氈的設計\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can scratch the peeling linoleum,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不想顯得太高階\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we don't want it to look too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓白人有種體驗下層生活的感覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want them white folks to feel like they slummin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是為了營造地道的氣氛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, to have an authentic atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就負責扮演黑鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I get to play the nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪  你也知道這種事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, Freddy, you know how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不只是來吃肋排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They don't just want the ribs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是要那種體驗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they want the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不用出市郊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but without having to leave the suburbs for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是賣燭光晚餐的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not selling candlelit dinners here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有決策都會經過你的首肯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}nothing gets built without your signing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要你出面否認    -否認戀情嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I need you to deny it.   - The affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀情  照片  所有這一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The affair, taking the photograph, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有公開來往的記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have a public history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾捐獻作品給...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I donated work for your...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以說那純粹是業務往來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can say we had a business relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你沒有給我拍躺在床上的照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but that you didn't take the picture of me in the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說是合成的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was Photoshopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever it is you need to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只印了一版  還在我這兒呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I only have one print and it's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個你也得銷燬掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦存檔也要刪掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The digital file also.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但刪之前先發給我們一份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But e-mail us a copy first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得確認照片裡沒有任何痕跡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to make sure that there's nothing in the image
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聯繫到你的工作室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that links to your studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都聽你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  亞當\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時在看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I watched you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你接受CNN直播採訪的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...when you did the CNN interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來打定主意不看的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I promised myself I wouldn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我忍不住\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要因為這種事才說上話真是遺憾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a shame it takes this for us to talk to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了這事  你還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're well, besides this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你來過之後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I spent three months in Colombia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去哥倫比亞工作了三個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}after you came up here to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也是逃避\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but also to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I met someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她來自波哥大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's from Bogotá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與當地非政府組織合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She was working with an NGO there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫伊奈茲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her name's Inez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們同居了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's living with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進展很快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Things happened quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  確實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. They did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該掛了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到指示前  我不能和媒體接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So I won't talk to the press until I get instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到你的聲音真好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's good to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-打完電話了    -嗯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You finished?   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘋狂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海洛因  可卡因  霹靂可卡因\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Smack, crack, blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來點吧  老頭  我們手裡應有盡有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, old man. We got what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不需要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要進門  就得買點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gotta buy somethin' if you want to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擋路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get out the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽的給我滾開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need to get the fuck on outta my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你鬧著玩而已  黑鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just fucking with you, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他媽的冷靜點嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Chill the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爺爺  開門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your grandfather. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在家辦公\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Work from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會把鬧劇帶去白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't need me dragging this circus to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說聲明打算怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean in terms of a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在起草  力求簡短有力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're drafting one, short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  弗蘭克  但我必須得問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, Frank, but you know I have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的  我會告訴你的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If it were true, I would tell you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要我發表公開聲明嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you like me to go on record?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說我支援你...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Say I stand beside--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  我很感激  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no, no. I appreciate that, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你不該為這種爛事髒了自己的手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you shouldn't dirty your hands with this sort of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果媒體逼問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the press corners you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們你不會搬弄是非\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just tell them you don't engage in gossip mongering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  嘉樂威先生好像要上電視了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, it seems Mr. Galloway is about to appear on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  有需要就告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go. Let me know if there's anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼好說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have very little to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一點  我從沒和克萊爾·安德伍德有過私情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only that I never had any romantic involvement with Claire Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有拍攝《特區日報》發表的照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and that I did not take the photograph printed in the DC Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  副總統夫婦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry that the vice president and his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得面對這種荒唐的折磨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}have to go through this ridiculous ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想請媒體不要把我和未婚妻捲入此事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I would ask that the media leave both my fiancée and me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小時內能準備好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll be ready in an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  會準備好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. We'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能得換身更...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You might want to change into something more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-保守的衣服嗎    -對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Conservative?   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先放點口風出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go throw the hounds a bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這很丟人...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know it's demeaning --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再多說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該更謹慎的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should have been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事就讓它過去吧  就像以前一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll put this behind us, just like we've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其實也挺希望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Part of me wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會更介意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That you'd be more upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克盯上你的原因是我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk came after you because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才有資格介意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's you who should be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浪費精力  對吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wasted energy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我倆來說都是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要事先排練一下嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shall we rehearse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你的幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是施捨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This ain't a handout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得慢慢還給我  給我打工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to pay me back over time. Work for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你打工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  我都會拿到房子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna get the house either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你住不住  那是你的選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whether you choose to live in it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我就需要這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, just what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐在安樂椅上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You in the easy chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次我進門出門都對我冷嘲熱諷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}laying into me every time I come in and out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子是給你和杜肖恩的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The place is for you and DeShawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我住我自己的公寓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna be at my own apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定那黑鬼不是在騙你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You sure this nigga ain't just sellin' you smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白紙黑字寫在合同裡  怎樣都有九萬五\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Says it right in the contract, 95 Gs no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五年沒見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Five years I don't see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻跑過來  說你弄到了九萬五\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then you come knocking on the door, talking about you got 95 Gs--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想再讓我去監獄裡見你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You didn't want me to visit you no more in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出來之後也不想見...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you sure didn't want to see me after you got out --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不想見你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I still don't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經站在這裡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去  老傢伙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get the fuck outta here, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You listen to me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直沒什麼可以給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I never had nothing to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有錢  我有的你也不想要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't have no money, and you didn't want whatever I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這可是一棟房子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we talking about a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜肖恩應該住在一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}DeShawn deserves to live better
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-比這裡更好的地方    -這不是為了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- than in a place like this.   - This ain't about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道去哪裡找我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有不到30分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Less than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要否認嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are they going to deny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓副總統和夫人自己來說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna let the Vice President and his wife speak for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們跟嘉樂威先生有聯絡嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have they been in contact with Mr. Galloway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, they haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們過了一整天才做出迴應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why has it taken them a full day to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你們肯定可以理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you can understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想先就誹謗與汙衊問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they wanted to consult with legal counsel first
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諮詢法律顧問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}regarding defamation and slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說他們要否認這段婚外情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're saying they will deny the affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說他們30分鐘之內就會出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm saying they'll be out here in 30 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以引述他們的話而不是我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you can quote them instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們的耐心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you all very much for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是恨死這個了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  等待嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What, waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  婚外情  都是狗屁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, the affair. It's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己就像個小報狗仔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I feel like a tabloid hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你寧願整天被困在白宮那邊嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'd rather be stuck at the White House all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fuck this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的寶貴時間做點有意義的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To do something meaningful with my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  幫我訂一張飛往聖路易斯的機票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, I need you to book me a flight to St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話最好是今晚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tonight, if you can find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問答環節  別費心提問了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No Q&A, so don't even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請大家規矩一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Behave yourselves, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有人懷疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I find it very painful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對我深愛的丈夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that anyone would suggest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有不忠行為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm capable of being unfaithful to my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我感到非常痛心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whom I love dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與亞當·嘉樂威已相識多年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've known Adam Galloway for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都認識他很多年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We both have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我負責淨水計劃時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I ran the Clean Water Initiative,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾委託他為營銷活動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I commissioned him to do a series of photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝了一系列攝影作品\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for the marketing campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他也極為慷慨地為我們的籌款拍賣會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he was extremely generous by donating work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捐贈了自己的作品\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for our fund-raising auctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不知道他為什麼要否認拍攝過這張照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So I'm not sure why he would deny taking the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡亞當的作品  所以讓他拍了這幅肖像\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I love Adam's work, so I asked him to take this portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裡拍的  就在這棟房子裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We did it here, at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝時弗蘭西斯就在旁邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis was there during the shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一份生日禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was a birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾問我想要什麼樣的肖像\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire asked me what sort of portrait I wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說就拍她睡著的樣子吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I said I want one of her sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她睡著的時候非常美\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because she's so very beautiful when she's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片就掛在我二樓的辦公室裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It hangs in my office on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're fucking lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只能猜測\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So I can only assume
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當被媒體的關注嚇到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that Adam was intimidated by the media attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}婚外情傳聞: 副總統與夫人出面迴應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想撇清關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and he needed to distance himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但真相其實就是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But really, all we have here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一位才華橫溢的攝影師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is a very talented photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這是一幅我們很喜愛的作品\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and a prized possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you all very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那樣看上去就太清白了  好像我們...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it would've seemed too clean otherwise, like we were--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我丟盡了臉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You made me look like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們說法一致\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we had the same story,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒體會認為我們是串通好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the media would assume we were coordinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須亂一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It needed to look messier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事本該結束的  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This was supposed to go away, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我樓外的記者多了一倍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got twice as much press outside the building now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Adam...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不把燈都關上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've gotta keep the lights off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們在對面樓頂上  想要拍我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}'cause they're on the roof across the street, trying to film us inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要證實照片是你為我們拍攝的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You just need to confirm that you took the photo for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證實我們的說法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Confirm our version.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你說謊是因為你害怕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Say you lied because you were scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你為什麼不事先\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know why you didn't just tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你要做的告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}this is what you were intending to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我瞭解你  你會拒絕的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I know you, and you would've refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自尊心太強了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have too much pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再面對媒體了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to speak to the press again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你什麼都不說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you say nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會放過你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they're not going to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會在外面守上幾星期\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They will just camp out for weeks on end--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...我覺得這樣不對  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is... it feels wrong, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我說謊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想擺佈你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't trying to be manipulative--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要掛了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他會想通的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think he'll do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  但願吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know. I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要來支菸嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我去睡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I'm gonna turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他上電視了叫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wake me if he goes on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-先生    -道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Sir.   - Doug,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和賽斯過來一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}why don't you and Seth come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要考慮起訴這家報紙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should we consider a lawsuit against the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表明我們不容忍這種八卦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Show we won't tolerate this sort of gossip?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會和解的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They won't settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們樂意上法庭  這樣能製造更多新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll fight it in the courts because it'll generate more news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統那兒呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what about the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他提出要表個態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He offered to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣熱度就更高了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Draws more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統發話不是個壞主意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}President isn't a bad idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們幫他起草講話稿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if we phrase a statement for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他成了頭條新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He becomes the headline
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們控制不了他的媒體策略\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we can't control his press operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們和他們協調好  就不會...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if we coordinate with them, it shouldn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協調會讓人生疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Coordination looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得讓人看不出痕跡啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So it's your job to conceal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果賽斯覺得總統的講話有弊無利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If Seth doesn't think the president should make a comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就相信他的判斷吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then we should defer to his judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再去拿瓶啤酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go get another beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你去拿吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can go grab you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我正想活動下手腳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I feel like stretching my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  來杯健怡可樂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug, diet Coke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fine, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯  來瓶啤酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth, a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還得開車  謝了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to drive, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就回\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我小心點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康納很容易扳倒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Connor was an easy target,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  能有這位置我已經很滿意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, doug, I'm grateful just to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在副總統身邊這麼久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think I've survived with the vice president
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這點小花招還看不出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so long by being blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給他們工作的晉升空間是有上限的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Upward mobility has a ceiling with the Underwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是上限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手裡還有他們什麼把柄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What else have you got on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你交出日記的時候沒留一手嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You fork over the journal without a backup plan for a rainy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼牌就出什麼牌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had one hand and I played it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會冒險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't press my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會指望我會相信吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't expect me to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒指望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換做我是你我也不相信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我說的是實話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟間的小鬥爭不是什麼壞事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A little sibling rivalry isn't such a bad thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在養子之間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}especially between adopted boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要麼彼此施壓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They either push each other
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都更上一層樓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to be the best versions of themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要麼其中一人被踢回孤兒院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or one of them gets booted back to the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝你們也得喝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You drink if I drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的健怡可樂  你的啤酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One Diet Coke for you, and one beer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的  真是一團糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, darling, what a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還撐得住嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒體接連騷擾了我們兩天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The press have been harassing us the past two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易離開公寓  差點被他們踩死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we barely made it out of the building without being trampled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, how awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說這兒有人要見我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said someone was here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在我辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告訴你他是誰了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did he tell you who he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在電話裡說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to say over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世道什麼都說不準\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You never know, these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他以前為安德伍德夫婦工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He says he used to work for the Underwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是誰    -你的助理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Who?   - Your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不  她不會...    -她會  她做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- No, she would never--   - She would and she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼目的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的老闆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The man I work for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這與你無關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在攪和我的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is my life you're fucking with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我都只是小卒  嘉樂威先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You and I are just pawns, Mr. Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要更多資訊...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來證明這事發生過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...to prove the affair happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一張照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Another photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你30秒  走出這扇門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thirty seconds, you better be out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認識這個國家區號嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You recognize the country code?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城市區號是波哥大的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the city code is Bogotá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒人接聽嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it still ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬歇爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Marshall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天  從沒見這裡這麼火\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Man, never seen it like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊都排到街上了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The line's down the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺壯觀  是吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Something else, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你需要人幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Looks like you could use some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後廚還有條圍裙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Got a extra apron in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹活兒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她賴在門廳不肯走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She refuses to leave the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉·薩伊德  《華爾街電訊報》的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ayla Sayyad, Wall Street Telegraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是副總統的記者團成員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's part of the Vice President's press corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫她上來吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Send her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了  特莉莎  我沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I appreciate it, tricia, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事鬧個一兩天也就過去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This whole thing will blow over in a day or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時我再\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能稍等下嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you hold on one second?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《日報》來電  他們要你發表評論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Daily. They called for a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當和他們談過了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did Adam speak with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談過了  但不是按我們的要求說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, but not what we told him to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把這個發給報社了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He sent them this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特莉莎  我能過會兒再打給你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tricia, can I call you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這是你嗎    -不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Is that you?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他說這就是你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because he's saying it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可能是    -安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- It might be.   - Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是  沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, it could be, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我特地問過你還有沒有別的把柄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I asked you about any vulnerabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他拍了這張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't know he took this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片裡你留著短髮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have short hair in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說過戀情兩年前就斷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said it ended over two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去年秋天去過他那兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I visited him last fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別人知道嗎  有誰在那兒見到過你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does anyone else know? Did anyone see you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他請朋友去過他的公寓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He had friends over, to his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們說過他是位朋友了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we've said that he's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拜訪他  參加聚會沒什麼問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's nothing wrong with me visiting him, being at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等這照片上了《日報》的頭版就有問題了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is if this photo is on the front page of the Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在中國  政治和生意是糾纏不清的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Politics and business are intertwined in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必你知道這一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as I'm sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了確保中央政府的許可\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not uncommon to partner
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結交有門路的合作伙伴很正常\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with someone who can ensure Beijing's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你需要他的政治影響力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you needed his political influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,費盡心機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All this is moot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的合作還是泡湯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our venture fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在傑斐遜港大橋獲批之後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right after the Port Jefferson Bridge was approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那項工程沒有任何關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had nothing to do with that project.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  馮也沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Neither did Feng, to my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有  但是吳彬陽投了資\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, but Wu Bin Yang did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是馮在北京的主要競爭對手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's Feng's biggest rival in Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我沒資格給你上中國政治課了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It looks like I shouldn't be schooling you on Chinese politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比我瞭解的多啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know far more than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用了"糾纏不清"這個詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You used the word "Intertwined."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是我對整件事的感受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's the sense I'm getting from all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核能補貼  中國精煉廠  大橋工程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The samarium subsidy, the Chinese refinery, the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及你和總統的關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}your friendship with the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰派你來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼派我來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who sent me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,財富積累到我這種程度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you're as rich as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就總得提防明槍暗箭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you're always a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己找來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你坐在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在聖路易斯採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是去報道副總統夫婦的醜聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Instead of covering the vice president and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得馮山德背後還有更多隱情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My gut says there's more to Xander Feng than has been reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是嗎    -把時間花在這上面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.   - It's a far better use of my time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比報道什麼八卦性醜聞更值得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than reporting on tabloid sex scandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是真正的新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not real news.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懷念德黑蘭了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You miss Tehran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在下面等待時  我讀了幾篇你的文章\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I read some of your work while you were in the waiting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那裡越來越危險了    -可不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- It started to get too dangerous.   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種環境不適合\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not the best place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.92,0:22:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚成家  生兒育女\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when you want to get married and start a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者猶太人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or if you're Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太去那兒旅遊時給我買了這個回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My wife got this for me when she visited there,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.28,0:22:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在伊斯蘭革命之前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before the revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,16世紀的古董\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}16th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託運回國的時候被弄碎了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It, um, broke when it was being shipped,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摔得粉碎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}into a thousand pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好幾名專家花了一年多才修復如初\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It took specialists over a year to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給  我希望你能收下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here, I want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能接受你的禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't accept gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  這不是禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no. Not as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是給你提個醒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. As a reminder of how hard it can be to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些東西一旦碎了  再拼起來就難了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}put something back together again once it's been crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想威脅我的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're going to threaten me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不用這麼兜圈子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you don't have to go to the trouble of veiling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一般不接受記者採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't usually do interviews with reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是寄生蟲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大都一心琢磨怎麼想辦法打擊我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Usually interested in just finding a way to knock me down a peg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自然而然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Invariably,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們寫的東西都不準確\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what they write is inaccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們不如實寫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不得不反擊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no choice but to retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國也可以像伊朗一樣危險  薩伊德小姐\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}America can be just as dangerous as Iran, ms. Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你抽時間見我  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your time, mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回華盛頓的路上注意安全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Travel safe back to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給雷米打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get Remy on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米在二線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remy's on line two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.42,0:24:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不要再留後手了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's not hold back on the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.50,0:24:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次打擊他  現在就執行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hit 'em again, and hit 'em now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.39,0:24:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收益最好的一天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Best day yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.75,0:24:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得弄個保險箱什麼的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You gotta get a safe or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者讓銀行上門收存款什麼的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or maybe one of those, uh, pickup services.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.68,0:24:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上帶這麼多錢走路太危險了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's too much money to be carrying around at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.58,0:24:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能應付\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對著槍口還怎麼應付\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There ain't nobody can handle a Glock to the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.94,0:24:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你自己有一把\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless you got one yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.49,0:24:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就不帶傢伙了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My days of packin' are long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來  拿我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There. Take mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.93,0:24:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家裡還有一把\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got one at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.39,0:24:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把那東西帶到這裡來幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What the fuck you doin' bringin' that thing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.08,0:24:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了安全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's just for protection, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.02,0:24:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道你為什麼要有槍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know what you doing with it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.14,0:25:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的假釋條例怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about your parole?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.42,0:25:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起假釋官我更擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm a lot more worried about niggas in my building
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.25,0:25:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家樓裡的黑鬼們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than some parole officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  坐下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.99,0:25:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  我說的就是這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See, man? This is what I'm talkin' about, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.48,0:25:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自以為是地評價我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You being all righteous and judgin' me and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我個面子  坐下  現在坐下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do me a favor and just sit down. Sit down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.89,0:25:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.60,0:25:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能遇到件好事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We got us a good thing, potentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.39,0:25:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能最終沒有結果  也可能會有好結果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe nothing comes of it, but maybe something does.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.50,0:25:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果連鎖店成功\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the joint works out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.22,0:25:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有一天你能當經理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}maybe one day you could be the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.96,0:25:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的火起來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shit, if it blows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.23,0:25:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能去經營整個連鎖店\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you could run the whole fucking franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.52,0:25:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那意味著你得小心點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that means you gotta be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.51,0:25:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再被抓回去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That means you cannot be sent back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.96,0:25:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得遵紀守法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We gotta follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.42,0:25:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.23,0:25:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.01,0:25:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會處理掉那東西嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You gonna get rid of that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.02,0:26:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.87,0:26:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.96,0:26:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才像個男人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now that's what's being a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.18,0:26:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你剪短頭髮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll need you to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.02,0:26:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多短\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How short?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.60,0:26:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼短\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This short.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.92,0:26:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還要做模特呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have a modeling career.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.27,0:26:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我剪那麼短\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I cut it that short--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真有模特工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you actually had a modeling career,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.10,0:26:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會在和你經紀人談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would be speaking to your agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.72,0:26:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是坐在你的公寓裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and not sitting in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.93,0:26:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想不想要這份工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you want this job or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}OK, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.18,0:26:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以剪短\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.35,0:26:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.31,0:26:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們去攝影棚之前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And before we go to the studio,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.87,0:26:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要知道你是否口齒清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to see how well-spoken you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.83,0:26:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.88,0:26:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你會出現在全美所有的新聞頻道上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because you're gonna be on every news channel in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  這是怎麼回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wait. What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.80,0:26:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀出這個  一字不差\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Read this. Those exact words.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.86,0:27:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Read 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.58,0:27:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有本事  就該背出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're good, you'll memorize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.21,0:27:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是斯特芬妮·道瑞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My name is Stephanie Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.69,0:27:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個職業模特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am a professional model.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.99,0:27:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪·海耶斯因在哥倫比亞高地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Freddy Hayes was convicted in 1982
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.34,0:27:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶劫一家便利店  而於1982年被定罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for sticking up a convenience store in Columbia Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.79,0:27:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在高速追捕中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}During a high-speed pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.11,0:27:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海耶斯失控撞向另一輛車\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hayes lost control and crashed into another vehicle,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導致一對老夫婦死亡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}killing an elderly couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.29,0:27:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對持械搶劫認罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He avoided manslaughter charges
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.76,0:27:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以免受過失殺人的起訴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by pleading guilty to armed robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.14,0:27:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他服刑九年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He served nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.57,0:27:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1992年他開了弗萊迪燒烤餐館\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In 1992 he opened Freddy's BBQ Joint,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.48,0:27:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一家專做肋排的小餐館\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a small restaurant specializing in ribs,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.54,0:27:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統弗蘭克·安德伍德是那裡的常客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}frequented by Vice President Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.90,0:27:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.59,0:27:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.40,0:27:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為是塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think it's Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.48,0:27:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.20,0:28:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德至賽斯·格雷森  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在給誰發簡訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who are you texting?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.65,0:27:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.40,0:28:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}賽斯·格雷森  攝影棚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.60,0:28:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  來我家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.97,0:28:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想釋出一份簡短聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I want to do is make a short statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.34,0:28:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪已經服過刑了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Freddy did his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.95,0:28:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他20年來一直遵紀守法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's been an upstanding citizen for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.13,0:28:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個殺死兩位老人的重罪犯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's a convicted felon who killed two senior citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.76,0:28:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是意外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}By accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.91,0:28:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是重點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that's beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.81,0:28:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不管他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am not gonna hang him out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.70,0:28:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有嘉樂威的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the Galloway story wasn't happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.39,0:28:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd say it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.75,0:28:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在太冒險了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it's too risky right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.73,0:28:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想這看起來像什麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Think of how this is shaping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.32,0:28:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個戴綠帽子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A vice president whose wife cheats on him
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.07,0:28:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還和前罪犯做朋友的副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and who is friendly with a former gang-banger?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.15,0:28:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你維護他不會有好結果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is no way you win standing up for this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.35,0:28:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他馬上要開連鎖店了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's about to start a franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.91,0:28:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不容許這事告吹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will not have it jeopardized
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.19,0:28:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為塔斯克決定針對...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because Tusk decides to come after --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.87,0:28:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不單是弗萊迪的問題  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is more than just Freddy, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.33,0:28:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做過調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did some digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.86,0:28:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他兒子因運毒和販毒坐過牢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His son did time for narcotics, trafficking, distribution--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.67,0:28:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒見過他兒子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never met his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.91,0:28:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事再緩緩  先解決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's hold off and tackle--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.26,0:28:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  明早安排我跟記者見一下面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I want you to organize a press avail tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.77,0:28:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派人接弗萊迪過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have Freddy brought over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.73,0:28:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從後門進\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bring him through the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.47,0:28:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.30,0:28:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對自己人見死不救\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't leave one of my own bleeding on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.18,0:29:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是華盛頓紅人隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're gonna have the Washington Redskins,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對手必須是紐約尼克斯隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then you're gonna have to have the New York Knickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}華盛頓紅人是美式足球隊  紐約尼克斯是籃球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.79,0:29:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  你完全弄錯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Pops, you ain't even deep like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開  夥計\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yo, back off, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.65,0:29:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都他媽滾開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Back the fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.71,0:29:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾  別理他們就好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Darnell, just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.58,0:29:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當我在開玩笑嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think I'm fucking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.69,0:29:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾  別理他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Darnell, ignore them! Ignore 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.48,0:29:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想被拍  他們就不能拍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They can't take our pictures if we don't want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.54,0:29:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子當然能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sure as hell can.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.99,0:29:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.89,0:29:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美國憲法第一修正案保護新聞自由
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.89,0:29:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一修正案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The First fuckin' Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.81,0:29:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽要給我講憲法嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You gonna read me the constitution now, motherfucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.92,0:29:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了  達奈爾  我們進去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, Darnell. Let's just go on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.81,0:29:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我和這混蛋還沒完\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nah, nah, I ain't done with this asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.05,0:29:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.37,0:29:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能威脅我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you can get all up in my face
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.69,0:29:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻不能威脅你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I can't get up in yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.85,0:29:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽你老爸的話  冷靜點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Listen to your daddy and chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.41,0:29:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾  我們走吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Darnell, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.35,0:29:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逼我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.32,0:29:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心我揍你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will fuck you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.58,0:29:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我怕你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think I'm scared of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.72,0:29:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕這個嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You scared of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.73,0:29:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾  你的保釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Darnell! Parole!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.62,0:29:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我你的名字嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.22,0:29:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯特芬妮·道瑞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stephanie Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名職業模特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm a professional model.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.35,0:29:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右邊照片裡的人是你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this is you in this photo on the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.41,0:29:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}安德伍德照片真實性遭質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.26,0:29:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.46,0:30:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道瑞小姐的這張照是昨天拍的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We shot this photo yesterday with Ms. Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.19,0:30:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說嘉樂威先生的照片是假的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you're suggesting that Mr. Galloway's photo is a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.70,0:30:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對專業攝影一無所知\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know anything about professional photography,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.47,0:30:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}賽斯·格雷森  副總統新聞發言人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.08,0:30:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個做宣傳的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just a flack.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.04,0:30:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們都能在24小時內偽造照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if we can create a fake in less than 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.56,0:30:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像亞當·嘉樂威那樣的專業攝影師...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think an expert photographer like Adam Galloway--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.62,0:30:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這指控相當嚴重\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those are serious allegations,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.98,0:30:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在嘉樂威先生極力否認的情況下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}especially given that Mr. Galloway vehemently denies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.55,0:30:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對他的否認並不意外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not surprised he's denying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.45,0:30:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過最後就是你們兩人對質了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ultimately, though, it's gonna be your word against his.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.00,0:30:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.60,0:30:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是美國的副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vice president of the United States'.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.06,0:30:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和一個可能有問題的人的對質\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's his word versus that of a potentially troubled man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.78,0:30:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.77,0:30:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Potentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.65,0:30:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許他是有動機的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or maybe he has a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.57,0:30:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉樂威先生會有什麼造假的動機呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What motive could Mr. Galloway possibly have for a fake photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.68,0:30:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能從中得到什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What would he get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.15,0:30:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.72,0:30:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是區分事實和虛構\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My job is to separate fact from fiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.87,0:30:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點和你一樣  坎迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just like yours is, Candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.86,0:30:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但或許對搞藝術的人來說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But maybe fact and fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.75,0:30:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實和虛構不那麼重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}don't matter as much to the artistic sensibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.19,0:30:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許他分得不那麼清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe the lines are blurred for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.90,0:30:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他並不拍攝虛構的作品\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is not a man who stages fictitious scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.49,0:30:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也說了  我不懂藝術\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like I said, the art stuff, it's over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.32,0:30:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許你是對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.33,0:30:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不願相信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I would hate to think
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.50,0:30:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉樂威先生這麼做僅僅是為了炒作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that Mr. Galloway was doing this just for publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.58,0:31:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這是炒作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think it's a publicity stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.02,0:31:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.55,0:31:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.19,0:31:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪在路上了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is Freddy on his way?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.81,0:31:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他兒子出事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There was an incident with his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.28,0:31:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.20,0:31:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他因持槍威脅攝像師被警方拘留\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's in custody for threatening a photographer with a firearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.39,0:31:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.69,0:31:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪現在在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where is Freddy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.84,0:31:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.09,0:31:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去看他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.62,0:31:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是貧困住宅區\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's the projects, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.49,0:31:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管  你看著辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't care, you figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.95,0:31:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不能讓媒體知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the press can't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.93,0:31:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.15,0:31:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯  我也很喜歡弗萊迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis, you know I love Freddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.13,0:31:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.12,0:31:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪很危險  因為你太在乎了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Freddy is dangerous because you care too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.49,0:31:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過在乎  會使人盲目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When we care too much, it blinds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.28,0:31:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克的做法太卑鄙了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What Tusk did is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.26,0:31:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻讓這事影響到你  這正是他的目的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you're letting it get to you, which is exactly what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.79,0:31:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我視而不見  無所作為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I ignore this, if I do nothing--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.02,0:31:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是無所作為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.82,0:31:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持專注也需要力量\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Staying focused requires strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.10,0:31:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我給你做點什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want me to make something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.99,0:31:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃吧  我不餓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You go ahead. I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.95,0:32:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得吃點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.94,0:32:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  這本來跟你無關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. You didn't ask for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.97,0:32:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對你不公平\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not fair to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.87,0:32:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想快點結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I want is to be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.16,0:32:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我父親平安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For my father to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.59,0:32:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我當時還有別的辦法...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I thought there was any other way, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.47,0:32:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想冒險讓他...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to take the chance that he would--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.01,0:32:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.08,0:32:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.70,0:32:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向知道他們很無情  但是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I always knew they were ruthless, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.00,0:32:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們像動物一樣關在這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're caged up in here like animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.98,0:32:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們把我刻畫成了那種...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're painting me as some sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.67,0:32:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你的家人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.29,0:32:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太殘忍了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.03,0:32:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們太他媽殘忍了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're fucking inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.65,0:32:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生氣也不能改變局面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Getting worked up isn't going to change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.35,0:32:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.09,0:33:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.97,0:33:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.83,0:33:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來看我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks for dropping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.74,0:33:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How you holdin' up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.09,0:33:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從沒見過你不穿西裝的樣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ain't never seen you without a suit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.35,0:33:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想太招人注意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We didn't want to draw too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.16,0:33:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  我的城堡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, this is it, my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.19,0:33:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你的大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ain't as big as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.28,0:33:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也夠用了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it'll do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.81,0:33:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盲眼威利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Blind Willie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.00,0:33:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}盲眼威利·約翰遜: 美國福音藍調歌手  吉他演奏家
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.76,0:33:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡藍調嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you a blues fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.41,0:33:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《漆黑的夜晚》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Dark Was the Night."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.38,0:33:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次聽都讓我陶醉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gets me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.13,0:33:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夥計  你早該告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Man, you shoulda told me that years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.04,0:33:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會即興演奏  聊起藍調能聊一整天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can jam, talking about some blues all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.78,0:33:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這張  78年原版\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Check this out. Original 78.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.82,0:33:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要喝點什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.85,0:33:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水  還是冰茶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Water? Iced tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.34,0:34:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要冰茶  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like some iced tea, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.93,0:34:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你兒子怎麼樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.34,0:34:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要六萬保釋金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They set the bail at 60 grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.99,0:34:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.23,0:34:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子怎麼樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's your wife doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.89,0:34:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾有一副三英寸厚的鎧甲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, Claire's got a suit of armor three inches thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.80,0:34:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些難關我們會撐過去的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll get through all this garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.53,0:34:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人想毀了你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Somebody's tryin' to take you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.26,0:34:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Appears that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.12,0:34:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whoever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.02,0:34:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們踩到不該踩的響尾蛇了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they done stepped on the wrong motherfuckin' rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.17,0:34:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我來這裡了  弗萊迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's why I'm here, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.15,0:34:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得遠離你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to distance myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.17,0:34:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要確保你不會到處宣揚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to make sure you're not going to play up
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.25,0:34:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是多好的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what good friends we've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.27,0:34:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你去過我的辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That you've been to my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.06,0:34:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還曾在我家做晚餐\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that you've cooked dinner at my home,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.25,0:34:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且總統也出席了那次晚餐\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or that the president was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.30,0:34:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能連累了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't drag him into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.63,0:35:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不會來吃肋排了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I won't be coming in for ribs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.39,0:35:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在出了這麼多事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With all that's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.49,0:35:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能再火上澆油了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we can't add fuel to the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.53,0:35:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是想來吃也吃不到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You couldn't if you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.28,0:35:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要賣掉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.71,0:35:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣掉餐館嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Selling the Joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.93,0:35:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.74,0:35:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.78,0:35:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醬汁的特許經營權什麼的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The franchise thing, with the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.97,0:35:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生意夥伴要解約了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My business partner's pullin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.38,0:35:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說他們銀泉的白人不喜歡去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Say them white folks down in Silver Spring don't wanna
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.00,0:35:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡棍開的餐館\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}go to no place run by thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.35,0:35:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼非得賣掉你的店\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why do you have to sell yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.02,0:35:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾的保釋金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Darnell's bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.47,0:35:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是無論如何都得給你十萬美金嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doesn't that guy have to give you a hundred grand, regardless?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.25,0:35:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我屁都拿不到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I ain't getting shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.79,0:35:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合同裡有一條道德條款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a morality clause in the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.93,0:35:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他打算花四萬五買我的門面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he's gonna pay me 45 thou for the storefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.80,0:35:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再加上我存的一點錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That with what little I got saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.24,0:35:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以付保釋金了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can pay that bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.57,0:35:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能把餐館賣掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't sell Freddy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.05,0:35:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經在起草合同了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's already drawing up the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.89,0:35:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你解決錢的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me help you with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.36,0:35:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nah, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.97,0:35:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當做是借貸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll make it a loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.77,0:35:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以以後再還我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.72,0:35:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.44,0:36:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別要強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't be prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.25,0:36:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-弗蘭克    -拜託  讓我幫你吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Frank.   - Please, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.67,0:36:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是內疚  我不會要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I ain't takin' your guilt money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.87,0:36:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去在道上的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I was bangin',
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.71,0:36:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一個月能賺六萬美金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we used to clear 60 Gs a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.46,0:36:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我見過同伴被人殘忍槍殺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I seen guys shot down execution-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.06,0:36:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一點也不關心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.11,0:36:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後我被捕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.15,0:36:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐牢的第一年裡達奈爾出生了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Darnell was born my first year in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.77,0:36:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一次也沒見過他  連照片都沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Never saw him once, not even a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.21,0:36:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能收回我所犯的罪惡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't take back the bad I done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.42,0:36:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做的就是一如既往\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I can do is to make my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.75,0:36:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過好自己的生活  你明白嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}like I've been doing. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.14,0:36:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要強  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ain't pride, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.22,0:37:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你改變心意了  就告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you change your mind, you let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.63,0:37:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是一個好顧客  僅此而已\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You was a good customer, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.14,0:37:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必假裝是我的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You ain't gotta pretend to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.19,0:37:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多保重  弗萊迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You take care of yourself, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You too, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.56,0:37:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我是一個偽君子嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think I'm a hypocrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.08,0:37:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就對了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.98,0:37:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會否認\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't disagree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.61,0:37:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通向權利的道路由虛偽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The road to power is paved with hypocrisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.01,0:37:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和犧牲鋪就\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...and casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.93,0:37:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不要後悔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Never regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.19,0:38:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.40,0:38:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐  亞當\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have a seat, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.78,0:38:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你按要求的那樣  把電話留在家裡了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You left your phone at home, as you were asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.55,0:38:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.11,0:38:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼跟你未婚妻說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what did you tell your fiancée exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.56,0:38:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說我要離開一陣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That I'd be gone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.01,0:38:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不知道我要去哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She doesn't know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.27,0:38:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人找到她  她會說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what will she say if someone checks in on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.17,0:38:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What will she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.88,0:38:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.12,0:38:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在得團結協作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to work together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.73,0:38:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試過  但你騙了我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I tried. You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:39:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我也解釋了為什麼要那麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I explained to you why that was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.82,0:39:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你不聽我的命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You didn't follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.37,0:39:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道雷米·丹頓是誰嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you know who Remy Danton is?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.89,0:39:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他找過你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.46,0:39:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈茲的父親是波哥大的一位人權運動家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Inez's father is a human rights activist in Bogotá.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.27,0:39:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府以叛國的罪名控告他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The government has charged him with treason
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.66,0:39:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與叛亂分子勾結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for working with the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.51,0:39:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要判他死刑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're going for the death penalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.73,0:39:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹頓說他們可以操縱法官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and Danton said they have the judge in their pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.99,0:39:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該來找我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should have come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.80,0:39:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.67,0:39:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹頓說你們什麼也做不了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Danton said you couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.96,0:39:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他錯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.15,0:39:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能冒險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't gonna take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.54,0:39:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父親如政府所稱那樣犯罪了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Has he done what the government's claiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.74,0:39:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  都是些無中生有的指控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. They're made-up charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.09,0:39:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是一個記者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's a journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.79,0:39:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報道達恩地塹那裡的殘暴行徑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}documenting atrocities in the Darien Gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.79,0:39:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}巴拿馬與哥倫比亞之間未開發的大片沼澤地
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.84,0:39:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以撤銷控告\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can get the charges dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.25,0:39:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我憑什麼相信你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.15,0:39:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為國務卿是我的好朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because the secretary of state is a good friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.40,0:39:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你別無選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.14,0:39:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是你的棋子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not your chess pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也不是遊戲  嘉樂威先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this isn't a game, Mr. Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.93,0:39:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼要耍我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why are you toying with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.04,0:39:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We are trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.92,0:39:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a fucking joke, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.24,0:39:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不準這樣和我妻子說話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do not talk to my wife that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.70,0:40:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子  那對你來說有什麼意義\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your wife. What does that even mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.84,0:40:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別因為你們之間有過一段歷史\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do not mistake any history you have shared
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.51,0:40:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就以為你瞭解我們的婚姻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for the slightest understanding of what our marriage is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.33,0:40:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是相比之下你是多麼無關緊要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or how insignificant you are in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.47,0:40:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我倆單獨談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you give us a few minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.71,0:40:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去給凱茜打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go call Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.48,0:40:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說我的工作和名聲吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Forget my career and my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.93,0:40:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和這個女人結婚  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to marry this woman, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.23,0:40:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會擺平這件事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're going to make this disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.12,0:40:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你  我將永遠是那個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because of you I will always be the man
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.81,0:40:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將她父親置於險境的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who placed her father in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.26,0:40:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這永遠無法抹去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can never erase that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.61,0:40:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉事情走到了這個地步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry it's come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.09,0:40:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真後悔遇見你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I ever met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.28,0:40:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從頭到尾  你只給過我痛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All you've ever done is cause me pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.51,0:40:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你又來破壞我的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now you're fucking with my life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.56,0:40:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我未婚妻的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the life of the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.57,0:40:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛她遠勝過愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that I love more than I ever loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.99,0:40:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚就開車回紐約\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll be driven back to New York tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.11,0:40:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天一早  你就發表聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the morning, you'll make a statement saying
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.73,0:40:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說這是炒作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}this was a publicity stunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.86,0:40:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的作品一直賣不出好價錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and that the value of your work had been stagnating
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.84,0:40:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你希望重振\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you wanted to revive--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.65,0:41:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  克萊爾  我才不會那樣做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, Claire. I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.86,0:41:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.89,0:41:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我去告訴記者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How about I tell the press--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.58,0:41:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當  閉嘴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Adam, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.66,0:41:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要說你想博取關注\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That you wanted the attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.22,0:41:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後又害怕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then you got cold feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.55,0:41:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否認了照片的事  接著又再次改了主意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}denied it, then you changed your mind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.06,0:41:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張浴室照片是你偽造的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that you faked the shower photo
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.04,0:41:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要澄清這一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you're coming clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.46,0:41:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.63,0:41:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被捲進這些事中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not part of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.07,0:41:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想攪進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't sign up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.00,0:41:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不感興趣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.95,0:41:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們給你提供了一條出路  亞當\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're giving you an out, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.41,0:41:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你選擇不接受的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you choose not to take it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.99,0:41:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會毀掉你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will bury you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.36,0:41:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒恨過任何人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never hated anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.52,0:41:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我知道那是什麼感覺了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now I know what that feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.81,0:41:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很糟  對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a terrible feeling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.44,0:42:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終止呼叫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}End call.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.77,0:42:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫已終止\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Call ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Call Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.94,0:42:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的住處沒人接電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No answer at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.22,0:42:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想要更多錢嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it a matter of more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.14,0:42:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國務卿杜蘭特已經致電莫里諾總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Secretary Durant has already called President Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.70,0:42:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們得趕快行動了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we need to move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.49,0:42:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外交部長已經牽扯進來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The minister of foreign affairs is involved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.80,0:42:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官不會在12小時內就宣判他有罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The judge isn't gonna rush a conviction in less than 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.86,0:42:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們認識什麼能跟部長說上話的人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who do we know who has the minister's ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.28,0:42:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人能夠比得過莫里諾總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody who can trump President Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.72,0:42:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他對杜蘭特對人權方面的看法非常敏感\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he's very sensitive to Durant's view on human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.67,0:42:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算放棄了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you giving up on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.93,0:42:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是現實一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Just being realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.00,0:42:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就做莫里諾的工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Work on Moreno then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.54,0:42:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快要被人察覺了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll start leaving footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.16,0:42:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.02,0:42:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說你  是我的鳥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, not you. My birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.95,0:42:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們要做好準備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think we need to be prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.41,0:42:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很可能沒法把威脅進行到底了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for the possibility that we can't follow through with our threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.45,0:43:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到的都是藉口  不是解決方案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am hearing excuses, not solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.14,0:43:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無能為力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.93,0:43:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法搞定整個美國國務院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't circumvent the entire US State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.43,0:43:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我僱你是為了讓你毀掉弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, I hired you to destroy Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.86,0:43:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要失敗了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.64,0:43:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  我是你的說客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, Raymond, I'm your lobbyist,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.27,0:43:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的走狗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not your henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.07,0:43:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我僱的不是說客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't employ lobbyists.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.28,0:43:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我僱的是對我有用的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I employ people who can be useful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.15,0:43:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你看起來沒用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you are proving otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.28,0:43:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.22,0:43:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.73,0:43:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.49,0:43:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  就這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.97,0:43:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.65,0:43:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我必須這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.83,0:43:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指控撤銷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The charges are dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.08,0:43:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們騙了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.96,0:43:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以騙他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can lie to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.11,0:43:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以提出新指控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}New charges can always be filed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.97,0:43:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能冒這個險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.48,0:43:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.66,0:44:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我感到失望嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you disappointed in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.54,0:44:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊把這事弄完吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's just get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.38,0:44:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}OK, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.47,0:44:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做出一項聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.58,0:44:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還需要一些掃尾工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There will be a little cleanup,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.74,0:44:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有一些人繼續關注這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}some folks who will want to linger on the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.32,0:44:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們已經渡過最困難的階段了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we're over the hump, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.60,0:44:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們現在可以出門了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we can leave the house now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.41,0:44:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越快恢復正常工作越好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The sooner you get back to normal work, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.49,0:44:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前被迫取消的會議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All the meetings I had to cancel,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.64,0:44:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法再做安排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}let's find a way to get them back on the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.18,0:44:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.79,0:44:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得繼續推動性侵法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to push ahead with the Assault Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.76,0:44:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們為您安排了明天和馬特·貝的採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've got your Matt Bai interview lined up for tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.89,0:44:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I think that--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.57,0:44:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們應該等事情平息之後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should hold off on Bai
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.47,0:44:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再考慮貝的採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}till after things quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.59,0:44:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才正打算這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's exactly what I was gonna suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.32,0:44:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格說得對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.06,0:44:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我們出發吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}OK, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.02,0:44:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在車裡等你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll meet you in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.94,0:44:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這些事處理得很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's done a good job handling all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.99,0:44:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.44,0:44:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們還要擔心什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should we have any more concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.54,0:44:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他沒有別的把柄了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He claims he doesn't have anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.65,0:44:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.87,0:44:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒到那個地步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.22,0:45:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盯著他點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.61,0:45:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正有此意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.80,0:45:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於雷蒙德  我們快速有力地回擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As for Raymond, we have to strike back hard and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.41,0:45:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打垮他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want him obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.42,0:45:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.69,0:45:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他受點折磨吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's make him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.59,0:45:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知我是該驕傲還是害怕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know whether to be proud or terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.86,0:45:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許兩者皆有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perhaps both.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.27,0:45:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我能多給你一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wish I could do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.21,0:45:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算拿她做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What you gonna do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.05,0:45:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒想好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.40,0:45:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許要把它拆掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Probably have to knock it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.07,0:46:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空地價值更高\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's worth more as an empty lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.06,0:46:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還有別的東西想拿走嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there anything else you wanna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.40,0:46:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀念品之類的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A memento or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.96,0:46:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.07,0:46:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一個向後看的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I ain't one for lookin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.82,0:46:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只向前看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Eyes ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.22,0:46:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運  弗萊迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good luck, Freddy.
